{"tid":2364782,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"認識廣東歌，由呢度開始！","createTime":"2021-01-13T08:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T15:12:17.000Z","uid":350760,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2e024c60514397553d34b44525f651530e242e78","tid":2364782,"uid":350760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:47:59.000Z","msg":"本來身邊好多朋友都無再聽廣東歌，但係近年本土意識開始抬頭，加上叱吒頒獎典禮之後好大迴響，令我發現廣東歌其實都仲有市場同討論空間！<br />\n但係今時唔同往日，接收音樂嘅媒介同渠道唔同咗，接觸廣東歌唔可以學似舊時咁靠電台電視台煮到埋嚟就食，自己都有責任主動發掘唔同歌手，幫助佢哋由獨立歌手嘅行列走上主流。<br />\n知道好多人對廣東歌嘅認識仲停留喺以前容祖兒、陳奕迅、人瑞、謝安琪嘅年代，所以想乘機介紹平時睇開嘅樂評Page俾大家。<br />\n利申：非打手，只係希望多啲人留意廣東歌。不過處女Post，有錯屌細力啲。<br />\n1. rs_cantopoppicks<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/rs_cantopoppicks?igshid=15hsskayull3b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Frs_cantopoppicks%3Figshid%3D15hsskayull3b&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=e2b72d18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/rs_cantopoppicks?igshid=15hsskayull3b</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6sQDnuP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6sQDnuP.jpg&h=e0e79601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分咗三個系列，R Pick新歌（新歌介紹），香港地誌遊蹤（用有香港街道或者地方命名嘅歌詞介紹返嗰個地方）同一對VS（兩首類近主題歌曲對比），啲圖都靚， 鍾意廣東歌啱曬。<br />\n2. anythinggoodlisten<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/anythinggoodlisten?igshid=187l83b6tjnip\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fanythinggoodlisten%3Figshid%3D187l83b6tjnip&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=8a588feb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/anythinggoodlisten?igshid=187l83b6tjnip</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3qZ8KJn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3qZ8KJn.jpg&h=4909afc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n專講新歌，分咗每週派台同每月推薦，顧名思義講下每星期最新嘅派台歌同每個月推薦邊幾首，記錄形式居多，資料都齊，文筆幾好，平時會跟佢介紹嚟聽，鍾意睇字啱曬。<br />\n3. listen.to.disc<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/listen.to.disc?igshid=os2gu825r18v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Flisten.to.disc%3Figshid%3Dos2gu825r18v&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=77538ffb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/listen.to.disc?igshid=os2gu825r18v</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bWm3yBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbWm3yBU.jpg&h=ac7ff6ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n專講廣東專輯，難得今時今日仲願意買實體大碟，然後逐首逐首歌評論，好有心。近排開咗Youtube Channel講專輯文化，鍾意買碟啱曬。<br />\n4. hk_songoftheday<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hk_songoftheday?igshid=1rx2ygz75ezwl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhk_songoftheday%3Figshid%3D1rx2ygz75ezwl&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=77b9131b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hk_songoftheday?igshid=1rx2ygz75ezwl</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hwu42vq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwu42vq.jpg&h=4bc690ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n專業樂評，詳細文字，會講下首歌以外嘅背景，介紹啲歌都幾高質，鍾意聽歌啱曬。<br />\n5. 9588hk<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/9588hk?igshid=71izjw3wd70a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2F9588hk%3Figshid%3D71izjw3wd70a&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=e7b18134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/9588hk?igshid=71izjw3wd70a</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2i7N0hh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2i7N0hh.jpg&h=fea9139f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nProduction好專業，Cover art又有心機，除咗介紹新歌仲有拍片同埋歌手現象分析，直頭將個Page當做音樂雜誌咁做，好多時睇完都學到嘢，鍾意音樂資訊啱曬。"},{"pid":"dec1b3b3bddd4f63a1424293a060fa9823d46e08","tid":2364782,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f04a1eac52c07b1ab6941cc51314366047dbc8","tid":2364782,"uid":385453,"like":0,"d